Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,8年前  2009a.t.b.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣布里塔尼亚帝国第十七王位继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修·Vi·布里塔尼亚大人觐见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说玛丽安娜王妃在布里塔尼亚宫殿被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里可不是恐怖分子能轻易进入的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  真正的犯人是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕  可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想试探这种事的内幕都令人恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是虽然母亲被杀了  他还是很坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是鲁路修大人已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幕后的阿修佛德家也完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的妹妹  那位公主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脚被射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛也受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说受了心理创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那身体可以用来当作政治的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲离开这个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢  这又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是为了说这种话才要求觐见布里塔尼亚皇帝的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,传下一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没空陪小孩子玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父皇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么您没有保护母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您是皇帝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个国家最伟大的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么应该能够保护她才对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也该见娜娜莉一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和弱者没什么好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是皇族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我也不要什么皇位继承权了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继承你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被卷入争斗也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你出生之时就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上穿的衣服到底是谁赐予你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住房  食物  连生命也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我赐予的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你从来没有靠自己活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  你却如此的愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经死了的你没有什么权利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你和娜娜莉一起交给日本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是王子和公主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以成为很好的交换道具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}击杀科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为第七代的KnightMare Frame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它的能力是一般机体的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那个Lancelot的机师是11区住民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让他从一等兵晋升到准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样让他满足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不靠编号住民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为是赌上性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才会有统治的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个道理我明白  皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连学校作业都要你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有上过普通的学校嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也让学生会的人教我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但总是无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始我还有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是弗兰克的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是担心你不能和同学亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来也做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那里碰巧有我以前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为他这个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好珍惜你那个朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个的友情能持续
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你们的再会就不是偶然了  而是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  那个你尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想听听你的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入手了很不错的蓝梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 解散解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没有出场机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭  喜  各  位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然今天的课已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友见面也是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我可以问你一件很重要的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲  你有没有隐瞒我们什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  不隐瞒下去也可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧  我不会惊讶的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上次我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和鲁路在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  上次你们在学校庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  那个是他擅自
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路擅自?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是上一次你也想要抓住这只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只是接吻这种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你们比那个还要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快停止你那奇怪的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你顾虑太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说关于相亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要重振阿修佛德家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  分裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琦玉平民区的包围完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山的东面是这条宇治川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,近邻居民有半数以上都在协助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于总成算影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次为-0.2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在预算范围内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是不是参加了那次新宿的镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  多亏科奈莉娅殿下的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有和你们说那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得很相似吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和新宿的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,军队部署在恐怖分子出没的琦玉贫民区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包围作战展开中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅总督为了限制出入人员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发布了禁止出入令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  那么可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎两个小时后会发动总攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  下一个区域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连时间都要报道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是在挑衅对方ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是一个冲动型犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了把他引出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意复制当时新宿的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他是那种自信过度的类型的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会想来杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来总督的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战争这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是互相争夺荣誉与生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打算接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她特地招待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我还有想问科奈莉娅的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏布里塔尼亚和找出杀死母亲的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你更重视哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚皇族为了下一任皇帝的宝座总在互相争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是被迫争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是布里塔尼亚强大的原因所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在争斗中取得胜利并活下来的最优秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将会成为下一任的皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者都会被弃之不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚就是这样的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱肉强食是最基本的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  娜娜莉算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为弱小所以不得不被放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会承认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把它消…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  我和鲁路修没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  鲁路修人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会知道  那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在履行和我的契约之前你死了  我会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的和做的不太一致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只射你的脚让你乖乖听话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能使用Geass吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  这也在预料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果自己能干的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会拜托我做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我会怕枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在遇见你之前一直都是死人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是无力的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说着我还活着这种谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不做的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是活着的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和平静的死亡没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让我回到像从前一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个贫民区的人不通报恐怖分子的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保护  隐藏他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这对国家来说是叛逆罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对负责人的清理工作已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还要考虑时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通报全军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始摧毁琦玉贫民区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全军  进入第一战斗态势
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么科奈莉娅殿下不命令我们出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有ORANGE在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被处分就该谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的错  我们的前途都被断送了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那是因为ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那个借口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然学生是协助者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,市外第四区镇压完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算克洛维斯变成科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪个部队的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报上你的部队名称及ID
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三侦查中队  达利奥·托雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从恐怖分子手中拿到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能帮忙联系一下总部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是光碟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在此之前先让我确认你的ID
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也想在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请你交出你的Sutherland
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  小心使用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外围不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不重整旗鼓的话根本无法突破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一带完全被压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小路也不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赤羽中将那里的援军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人还好说  团队是根本不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,户田和川口方面怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那些  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿的事想必你们也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,服从我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话你们就能获救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B0区镇压完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,F7区未发现敌踪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,D24…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,博瓦顿队向516方向转移
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向516转移
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没来吗  叫ZERO的那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是区区的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了  真的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和ZERO说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把科奈莉娅引出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,创造机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R1 R2原地后退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把敌人引到N2的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7向两点钟方向射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P5的队伍开始向正面射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯塔队失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,G47方面发现敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西斯基队正与敌方交战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎中了伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人似乎捕获了我军的Sutherland \N现在正在使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和新宿的时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了吗  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N2就这样向右上方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R4射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N1目标是左边那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P3  把桥打下来把路截断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,17点被攻下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里队失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向全军发出撤退的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再多的损害是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斗胆进言  我们还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可打不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向贫民区外延撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,队形不要乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向贫民区外延迅速移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没有紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要混在撤退的部队里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅  很快就可以到你的附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,条件这么快就备齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血缘真是不可否定的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个类型很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟会通向哪条路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来鲁路在这个地区创立之前就来这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是邻居吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路看上去总是不认真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和努力这种东西完全没有缘分似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话一开始我一点也不喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高一的时候我目睹了一起交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都是后面撞上来的人不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谁也没有帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路他呢 没有赞同那个人的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有一笑置之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是像往常一样一幅很无聊的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我突然想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底在考虑什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然想要了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,输的会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赢的会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督是胜利的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的骑士吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵照您的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我有Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在通常的警备条件下入侵还是太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是要像克洛维斯那时一样创造机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,商量关于猫祭的事应该是在明天才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然卡莲说不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我总觉得她是为了蒙混过关才装生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这种时候还是要问本人比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便也问问他怎么看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  一定会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让我做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真拼命啊  科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以为亲卫队能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有N1恢复识别信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为布里塔尼亚机行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现发出信号的一架KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被留在市外区域了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能进行通信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出动救护队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把它破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能成为敌人的人质了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经下令撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法执行命令的士兵是不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算舍弃生命也要完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我的部下来说这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你们不明白识别信号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是己方的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,N2  发射信号并往医院方向撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R1  R2在那里埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击追来的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是信号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方有伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,格罗斯塔增援  包围他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,R1  R2  中止埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,格罗斯塔到达指定地域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发现敌踪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,预测到这边的行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定对方真的是ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P2  N3  向敌人后方迂回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  赶快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P2  N3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  B1  B5你们两个上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是科奈莉娅的亲卫队 怎么可能会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们投降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,P6  P8怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7  迂回到N4那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是B7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现敌方猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先把对方干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7  服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不干的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,退下  他们从上面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B7  服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B8  报告现在的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B8
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的人按照顺序报上你们的编号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作战完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全军集中到第四方阵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被镇压了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没构成游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能像新宿那么顺利呢  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说这只是模仿他手段的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  很快就会清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是组织
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差别太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全部KnightMare的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打开舱门露出你们的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部机师都打开舱门露出你们的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被检查的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有ZERO的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真正身份也会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不直接看着对方是没有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人在KnightMare里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让其他机师保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的人数太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能让他们都面向这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  也许可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要自称是ZERO的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样的话  KnightMare就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  先下手攻击强制突破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以科奈莉娅的亲卫队为对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是自杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  赶快打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  在刚才的战斗中舱门被卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  那我来帮你打开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回过身来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO 发现ZERO了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然ZERO是这种性格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把他抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三  第五小队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速捕捉  确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把他包围起来  你们绕到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狙击部队  射击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是圈套的可能性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道到底是不是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能确认的只有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就如总督的分析他是个自尊心极强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么追也是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故意把自己的身形暴露在敌人面前  也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要确保逃走路线之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明哲保身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和克洛维斯不是一个等级的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是科奈莉娅吗
